**Addendum III:** Initial Encounter

[[div class="blockquote"]]
**Foreword:** The following is a transcript of body camera footage recovered from the scene of the first documented encounter with Item 8554, on 18/05/2023. Prior to this encounter, Foundation analysts intercepted a second anomalous message bearing the signature of Dr. Wondertainment, containing the coordinates of the location. At the time of the encounter, no dedicated containment protocols for Item 8554 had been established. MTF Kappa-20 ("The Collectors") was founded as a direct response to this incident.

-----
= **[BEGIN LOG]**

//[Three Foundation agents— Agent Dominguez, Agent Cruz and Agent Villalobos — approach an abandoned industrial warehouse on the outskirts of São Miguel dos Milagres. Agent Dominguez leads; Agents Cruz and Villalobos flanks. Weapons are drawn.]//

**Agent Dominguez:** Command, we have visual on the structure. Proceeding inside.

**Command:** Copy that. Proceed carefully.

//[All agents enter the warehouse. Interior lighting is minimal. A figure is visible at the far end of thre room, standing with its back to the agents. Both of the figure's hands appear to be skinless.]//

**Agent Dominguez:** Subject's been located. //[To Item 8554]// Hands where I can see them, now!

//[The figure turns slowly. Item 8554 regards the agents without visible agitation.]//

**Item 8554:** Finally, Foundation agents. I was wondering when you would find me.

**Agent Cruz:** Do not move!

**Agent Dominguez:** Keep your hands where we can see them. You are now being tken into Foundation custody.

**Item 8554:** I don't think so.

**Agent Villalobos:** Sir, hands visible now—

**Item 8554:** I am not your enemy, but I won't go with you.

**Agent Dominguez:** That's not a request. Stand down

//[A pause. Item 8554 looks down at its hands.]//

**Item 8554:** Do you know what I could do before all of this? I could heal. Fractures, deterioration — I could fix what was broken. They found out, of course. Árida Labs. Small operation, quiet. Nobody looked twice at them. Not even you.

**Agent Cruz:** Command, subject is non-compliant, requesting—

**Item 8554:**  They used me for two years. Experimental treatments, pharmaceutical trials. I was useful to them, so they kept me useful. When I stopped being useful they would have disposed of me.

**Agent Dominguez:** And then the curse came. Suddenly, I was not useful anymore. I was dangerous. So they tried to dispose of me early.

//[Item 8554 glances at Agent Villalobos.]//

**Item 8554:** I do not enjoy what I am now. But I prefer it to what I was.

//[Agent Dominguez advances toward Item 8554. Item 8554 steps aside and makes brief contact with Agent Domingez's forearm. Agent Dominguez collapses immediately. Agent Cruz opens fire; Item 8554 sustains two gunshot wounds to the torso without visible effect and makes contact with Agent Cruz's shoulder. Agent Cruz collapses as well.]//

**Agent Villalobos:** Command, we have two down, I repeat, two agents down—

//[Item 8554 turns to Agent Villalobos. A pause.]//

**Item 8554:** Tell your Foundation that Mr. Message sends his regards. He knows you have been looking for him since Shadows escaped, and he wanted you to know that as well.

**Agent Villalobos:** And what the hell does that mean?!

**Item 8554:**  It means you found me because he allowed it. Consider carefully what that implies before you continue looking.

//[Item 8554 exits through a rear access point. Agent Villalobos does not pursue it.]//

= **[END LOG]**

-----
**Afterword:** Agents Dominguez and Cruz were recovered from the scene and transferred to Foundation medical facilities. Both subjects survived; complete restoration of osseous tissue has not been achieved. FA-03 sustained no physical injuries. A copy of Document 8554/A was recovered from a table within the warehouse following Item 8554's departure. Following this incident, Mobile Task Force Kappa-20 ("The Collectors") was established and assigned exclusively to the location, study, and apprehension of anomalies associated with this New Little Misters series.
[[/div]]

