**Addendum V:** New Reports

As of 24/03/2026, several casualties similar to that found on the Árida Labs premises were located near Facility 09 at a common grave. Some of this casualties have been identified as a large amount of Foundation personnel who was reported as missing no more than 3 months ago. Is suspected that there are at least 30 out of 46 casualties of Foundation personnel; the rest of the casualties were identified as follows: 9 ex-employees of [[[https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/prometheus-labs-hub|Prometheus Labs]]]; 4 [[[https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/unusual-incidents-unit-hub|FBI's UIU]]] field Agents; and 1 civilian. As a response to this events, MTF Kappa-20 has been partially stationated at Facility 09 to locate and retrieve Item 8554 to Facility 04. At this point, the localization of "Mr. Message" is of top priority.

